### Bootstrap admin (com header secreto)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/bootstrap
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Secret: codice-seed-dev-secret

{
  "email": "maria@email.com"
}

### Login do admin (recebe token com isAdmin=true)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### GET /admin/listings?status=PENDING_REVIEW (com token admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/listings?status=PENDING_REVIEW
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### POST /admin/listings/{id}/approve
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/listings/{{listing_id}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### POST /admin/listings/{id}/pause
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/listings/{{listing_id}}/pause
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "note": "foto ruim"
}

### POST /admin/listings/{id}/resume
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/listings/{{listing_id}}/resume
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### POST /admin/seed com token de admin (esperado: 200)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/seed
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### POST /admin/seed sem token (esperado: 401)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/seed

### GET /admin/seed (esperado: 405)
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/seed
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### GET /admin/listings sem token (esperado: 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/listings

### GET /admin/listings com token nao-admin (esperado: 403)
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/listings
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
